<info gid="2536623223" type="Plot Summary">The new anime takes place in &quot;Crest Land,&quot; where the mysterious &quot;B-Crystal&quot; has started to go berserk. The main protagonist Kamon Godai lives in the south area of Crest Land, and is an energetic boy who loves B-Daman. However, he lost his all past memories of B-Daman and his family, except for his big sister Aona who lives with him. One day, Kamon meets Galvan, a B-Daman at his local B-Daman shop, &quot;B-Junk,&quot; and he finds Galvan strangely familiar. Galvan becomes his partner, and he returns to the B-Daman battles once again.</info>
